## Recommendation Summary

### Intent Assessment
Tutorial showing how to use Dagre for automatic hierarchical graph layout within Svelte Flow. Contains a complete code example for node positioning, edge routing, and layout direction toggling. Directly relevant to beestgraph web UI.

